body:
Support struct init, from sv_tests 7_2_2_struct_init.  Working on this isn't a priority, please make a comment if this is blocking real code.

```
   struct {  // Can't legally be packed
      bit [3:0] m_lo = P;
      bit [3:0] m_hi;
   } s;
```

